# Telegram notifications for the application form.
# 1. Create a bot with @BotFather and copy the token below.
# 2. Send any message to your new bot (or add it to a group).
# 3. Open https://api.telegram.org/bot<TOKEN>/getUpdates and copy the chat id.
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=
TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=
